casebody.data:
Robert Lynn PRUETT, petitioner,
v.
Jack CHOATE, et al. No. 17-6312 (17A390). Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 12, 2017.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice ALITO and by him to referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
